OL,4,CCity drivers 'should think twice'
OL,5,Cbefore buying SUVs
OL,6, Drivers in crowded cities should think
OL,7, twice before buying a big SUV, says the
OL,8, head of a motoring organisation.
OL,10,FSteve Gooding, from the RAC Foundation,
OL,11,Fsaid: "We should all choose the right
OL,12,Fvehicle for the right trip to cut the
OL,13,Fsize of our carbon footprint.
OL,15,F"It is right to question if suburban
OL,16,Fdrivers need a car capable of ploughing
OL,17,Fover rivers, across fields and up steep
OL,18,Fhills just to pop to the shops."
OL,20,FHis comments come as research confirms
OL,21,Fmost SUVs are bought by urban drivers.
